[
    {
        "content": "<p>What is the most appropriate method to produce <code>2pi</code> in single precision? Do we need to explicitly convert from the double precision result?</p>",
        "id": 223253696,
        "sender_full_name": "Júlio Hoffimann",
        "timestamp": 1611074510
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I have geometric algorithms with angles that need to do <code>2pi - theta</code> and this is creating some type instabilities in single precision when theta is single</p>",
        "id": 223253832,
        "sender_full_name": "Júlio Hoffimann",
        "timestamp": 1611074550
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>So my question is: is there a method to convert the irrational pi to a single precision float directly?</p>",
        "id": 223254006,
        "sender_full_name": "Júlio Hoffimann",
        "timestamp": 1611074634
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>Float32(pi)</code></p>",
        "id": 223254175,
        "sender_full_name": "Fredrik Ekre",
        "timestamp": 1611074707
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yes, I guess that is the best option <span aria-label=\"smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f642\" role=\"img\" title=\"smile\">:smile:</span></p>",
        "id": 223254883,
        "sender_full_name": "Júlio Hoffimann",
        "timestamp": 1611075038
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>there's always </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Julia\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">julia</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"mf\">2f0</span><span class=\"nb\">π</span>\n<span class=\"mf\">6.2831855f0</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 223255169,
        "sender_full_name": "Mason Protter",
        "timestamp": 1611075151
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>cool trick too <span aria-label=\"smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f642\" role=\"img\" title=\"smile\">:smile:</span></p>",
        "id": 223256100,
        "sender_full_name": "Júlio Hoffimann",
        "timestamp": 1611075506
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>but in this case I need to be generic with a type <code>T(pi)</code> inside a function</p>",
        "id": 223256153,
        "sender_full_name": "Júlio Hoffimann",
        "timestamp": 1611075531
    },
    {
